title: [1508521049] Best North African Restaurant: Azou's Big Test - Gordon Ramsay
description:
North African restaurant, Azou, get put to the test by having to serve food in Gordon Ramsay's Restaurant, and impress 20 esteemed guests.

Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title.
